{"tid":184102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：退休即是等死","createTime":"2017-04-02T14:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T15:25:58.000Z","uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2cc8ef9f14acdf176caa5974910b69a144d1136","tid":184102,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴領隊雲格依然不想退休，雖然他在球隊的未來仍然未公布，但是他表明退休只會無所事事。<br />\n<br />\n67歲的雲格依然有意繼續執教生涯，不過球迷反對聲音越來越強烈。<br />\n<br />\n雲格說無論如何他都想來季繼續工作，未理會是什麼崗位，因為他不想人生就此停下來。<br />\n<br />\n雲格一邊盛讚費格遜的功績，一邊說明自己不想離場：「<span style=\"color: red;\">想退休是年輕人的想法，對於老一輩來說，退休意味等死。</span>我至今依然為足球比賽著迷，盡量觀看每場比賽，實在是趣味無窮。我的飢渴程度與以往一樣，也許肩上的擔子重了，但對於足球的熱愛始終如一。」<br />\n<br />\n「你看看阿仙奴今天發展是多麼美好！以往阿仙奴一股是400鎊，現在是18000鎊，但我一股也沒有的！對於比賽，臾也討厭失敗，球迷也討厭失敗，唯一取勝方法是球隊球迷都團結一致，每場比賽戰鬥到底，這就是我們所能夠做到的事情了。我執教了34年，腦海中仍然想著如何擊敗對手。」雲格強調。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=aac4bc28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班人想雲爺爺死"},{"pid":"c120f275cd80bf89f6d0b02ac3e0ae25ee3b5632","tid":184102,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9ab0fa9e0de53d789f2cf387084d7175e0f917","tid":184102,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"暗串我地費sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e3801481a13b814e0f43aed341b01822032c7b","tid":184102,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:46:09.000Z","msg":"你看看阿仙奴今天發展是多麼美好！"},{"pid":"6cf692e3a9f60c36acbbf2f270c2632f1a0753b8","tid":184102,"uid":661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:47:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母睇波翻屋企睇啦"},{"pid":"e792d7b44f8f2a6f798bba319bd163fedb2a4844","tid":184102,"uid":48142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:50:18.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"5d392c1680daa4cf5931034e8eb066b9c9d08cc7","tid":184102,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04df9bf90e9466ed59e111e857d326b7ed7c8ee1","tid":184102,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"廢蛇退休都要躺槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5741651505f77ad5c53ee04833981ea1eecac59a","tid":184102,"uid":67432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"咁又係 又離咗婚 無家庭生活 唔返工真係等死 不過可唔可以死遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466402833574f359fbad7e7e29a04862c9a18117","tid":184102,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"無錢先係<br />\n你咁撚有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}